<ol class=3D"arabic">
<li><p>Replace any transpose operations with the conjugate of the transpose=
.</p>
<div class=3D"highlight-pycon3 notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight"><pre i=
d=3D"codecell4" tabindex=3D"-1"><span></span><span class=3D"gp">&gt;&gt;&gt=
